Slurm

```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "software": [
    "openmpi",
    "anaconda3",
    "julia",
    "python3"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "nodes": 4,
    "time": "08:00:00",
    "queue": "normal",
    "job_name": "s3",
    "email": "nkozak@stanford.edu",
    "email_type": "ALL",
    "output_file": "s3.%j.out",
    "conda_environment": "env_CS238",
    "working_directory": "/home/nkozak/CS238/explore_states",
    "script": "s3.py"
  },
  "other_commands": [
    "tail -n 1000 s3*.out > end_s3.out",
    "rm s3*.out",
    "rm -r 1*",
    "rm -r 2*",
    "rm -r 3*",
    "rm -r 4*",
    "rm -r 5*",
    "rm -r 6*",
    "rm -r 7*",
    "rm -r 8*",
    "rm -r 9*",
    "rm -r processor*",
    "zip -r VTK.zip VTK",
    "rm -r VTK",
    "zip -r postProcessing.zip postProcessing",
    "rm -r postProcessing",
    "mkdir /scratch/users/nkozak/CS238/explore_states/s3",
    "mv /home/nkozak/CS238/explore_states/s3/backGround /scratch/users/nkozak/CS238/explore_states/s3/."
  ]
}
```
